thread.title_full: Frenzy play of the week- Week 5 - WCAX.COM Local Vermont News, Weather and Sports-

author: Scott Fleishman
title: Frenzy play of the week- Week 5
text:
With over 56 percent of the vote, Brattleboro's Taylor King wins the Friday Football Frenzy Play of the Week for week 5. King made an incredible spinning grab, while somehow keeping his feet inbounds for a 24 yard touchdown.
Kings catch beat out a great grab by MSJ's Jonah Farrow and a one handed snag by South Burlington's Colby Barrett.
